    dc:description "Figures 75, 76. Neobonzia key illustrations 75 a Sensilla at and pt clavate, short, length less than the width of the proterosomal shield 75 b Sensilla at and pt clavate, long, length greater than the width of the proterosomal shield 75 c Sensilla at and pt normal, not clavate 76 a Coxae I-II nearly touching medially 76 b Coxae I-II widely separated medially." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29904" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

